node.text: Our Super Bowl commercial debut is a heartfelt message from Bass Pro Shops founder Johnny Morris inviting everyone to, “Get Back to the Nature.” See you out there.

Sometimes natures gives you a little more than you were looking for. 📸 :@Leocervantes11 

"We were hunting in Colorado and it had just snowed. I was posted waiting for elk to come in, but these bucks decided to come say hello! They didn’t notice me till they were almost eating my foot."

node.text:
Let's take a trip back to the good ol' days of fly-fishing when you tied your own flies and hit the streams and rivers to test your creations. Grab your materials at the link in our bio and join us as we tie up our fly of the month, the Winged Ant.

Required Materials:

Recommended Hook: Standard Dry Fly, sizes 12-16

Recommended Thread: Black 6/0

Recommended Body: Black Superfine Drubbing

Recommended Wings & Hackle: Brown Dry Fly Grade (match hook size)

node.title: September Fly of The Month- The Winged Ant

node.text: The silver kings. Tarpon are widely regarded as the ultimate inshore game fish and are vital to the fishing and tourism industries in coastal areas along the Atlantic and the Gulf of Florida. However, their populations are rapidly decreasing. Our partnership with the @Bonefishtarpontrust is focused on a better understanding of these amazing fish and their behavior to ensure that they will be around for generations to come.
